
// This Hyperlambda code snippet replaces placeholders within a string with actual values. The [set-value] slot updates the value of the [.body] node by using the [strings.replace] slot to substitute occurrences of "{{name}}" in the [.body] node with the value retrieved from the [.arguments] node's [name] child. The [get-value] slot fetches the value of the [name] node within [.arguments].
set-value:x:@.body
   strings.replace:x:@.body
      .:{{name}}
      get-value:x:@.arguments/*/name
